  - health score included
  - Family Care recipient limit = 5
  - API exact payload fixed
  - UI exact display fixed
  - DB / API / UI consistency fixed
  - privacy / audit / permission gate fixed

next_stage_note:
  - 実装する場合は change request なしでこの設計を起点にしてよい




